column16: Ryan Howard out on a sacrifice fly to right fielder Nick Markakis.   Odubel Herrera scores.    Cesar Hernandez to 3rd.

Clint Robinson walks.   Bryce Harper to 3rd.    Wilson Ramos to 2nd.
Dana Eveland intentionally walks Wilson Ramos.

Yunel Escobar grounds out, shortstop Andrelton Simmons to first baseman Kelly Johnson.
Bryce Harper grounds out softly, first baseman Chris Johnson to pitcher Dana Eveland.
Travis Shaw grounds out to first baseman Kelly Johnson.
Pablo Sandoval doubles (8) on a fly ball to center fielder Cameron Maybin.
Xander Bogaerts homers (3) on a fly ball to center field.
Travis d'Arnaud grounds out, shortstop Andrelton Simmons to first baseman Freddie Freeman.

Lucas Duda doubles (19) on a line drive to center fielder Cameron Maybin.   Travis d'Arnaud scores.
